  "detailed_description": "Have fun with a pixel art puzzle game. and minimalist with 100+ levels.<br>Play and discover all the paths the ball will take to pass the level.<br><br>Click on the cannon to shoot the ball.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/2484c57b1319f7356e07b9d39b75a5ff.poster.avif?t=1692033628\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/2484c57b1319f7356e07b9d39b75a5ff.webm?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/2484c57b1319f7356e07b9d39b75a5ff.mp4?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To rotate the obstacles just click exactly on top of them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/06aae297171153cc43be99999aaf52c1.poster.avif?t=1692033628\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/06aae297171153cc43be99999aaf52c1.webm?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/06aae297171153cc43be99999aaf52c1.mp4?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You need to place all the platforms correctly, if not, the ball might get lost on the way. One click can make a difference!!!!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/9afbeab461a2a992ca1522ad5c73497d.poster.avif?t=1692033628\" width=576 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/9afbeab461a2a992ca1522ad5c73497d.webm?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/9afbeab461a2a992ca1522ad5c73497d.mp4?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will have several challenges throughout the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/fe394f14e39d45d74fd8645e2c8447f9.poster.avif?t=1692033628\" width=576 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/fe394f14e39d45d74fd8645e2c8447f9.webm?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/fe394f14e39d45d74fd8645e2c8447f9.mp4?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Not everything always follows a single path, sometimes if you think a little more, you can find other paths.",
  "about_the_game": "Have fun with a pixel art puzzle game. and minimalist with 100+ levels.<br>Play and discover all the paths the ball will take to pass the level.<br><br>Click on the cannon to shoot the ball.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/2484c57b1319f7356e07b9d39b75a5ff.poster.avif?t=1692033628\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/2484c57b1319f7356e07b9d39b75a5ff.webm?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/2484c57b1319f7356e07b9d39b75a5ff.mp4?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To rotate the obstacles just click exactly on top of them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/06aae297171153cc43be99999aaf52c1.poster.avif?t=1692033628\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/06aae297171153cc43be99999aaf52c1.webm?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/06aae297171153cc43be99999aaf52c1.mp4?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You need to place all the platforms correctly, if not, the ball might get lost on the way. One click can make a difference!!!!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/9afbeab461a2a992ca1522ad5c73497d.poster.avif?t=1692033628\" width=576 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/9afbeab461a2a992ca1522ad5c73497d.webm?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/9afbeab461a2a992ca1522ad5c73497d.mp4?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will have several challenges throughout the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/fe394f14e39d45d74fd8645e2c8447f9.poster.avif?t=1692033628\" width=576 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/fe394f14e39d45d74fd8645e2c8447f9.webm?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929330/extras/fe394f14e39d45d74fd8645e2c8447f9.mp4?t=1692033628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Not everything always follows a single path, sometimes if you think a little more, you can find other paths.",
